    "Finally, secure cloud communication protocols and encryption techniques were used to protect sensitive sensor data from unauthorized access and cyber-attacks.",
    "Online anomaly detection with energy-efficient techniquesThe Online Anomaly Detection algorithm detects anomalies in real-time streaming data from wireless sensor nodes.",
    "It continuously analyzes incoming data, making it ideal for time-critical applications in resource-constrained environments.",
